OL,3,CScotland have 'really good prospects'
OL,4,Cfor World Cup, says optimistic Swinney
OL,6,FJohn Swinney has said that Scotland
OL,7,Fhave "really good prospects" in the
OL,8,Fforthcoming Fifa World Cup.
OL,10,FThe First Minister said he is "very
OL,11,Foptimistic and very excited" to see
OL,12,Fhis country's team take on Haiti at
OL,13,Fthe Boston Stadium in Foxborough,
OL,14,FMassachusetts, on June 13.
OL,16,FMr Swinney, who was speaking ahead of
OL,17,Ftravelling to the US for the
OL,18,Fcompetition, was on a visit to Hampden
OL,19,FPark, Glasgow, where he met with youth
OL,20,Ffootballers and enjoyed a tour of the
OL,21,Fstadium's football museum.
OL,26,@oD@FOUoD@\O]rD@_OUsD@\O]
