OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781222570
OL,3,CScotland have 'really good prospects'
OL,4,Cfor World Cup, says optimistic Swinney
OL,6,FHe told the Press Association: "I've
OL,7,Fnever seen Scotland in the World Cup,
OL,8,Fother than at home.
OL,10,F"I'm looking forward to being there, I
OL,11,Fcan scarcely believe that I'm actually
OL,12,Fgoing to be at a World Cup game that
OL,13,FScotland's going to be playing, and
OL,14,Fit's part of an exciting moment for
OL,15,Fthe country.
OL,26,@nD@`OUrD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781222570
OL,3,CScotland have 'really good prospects'
OL,4,Cfor World Cup, says optimistic Swinney
OL,6,F"I think everyone has been looking
OL,7,Fforward to this after the success
OL,8,Fagainst Denmark and the certainty of
OL,9,Fqualification and, of course, the
OL,10,Fevents leading up to this are
OL,11,Fsignificant."
OL,13,FHe added: "So, I go into this very
OL,14,Foptimistic and very excited."
OL,16,FMr Swinney later donned a Scotland
OL,17,Fjersey to pose for a photo in front of
OL,18,Fthe new Scott McTominay mural outside
OL,19,Fthe stadium.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@MO]uD@KOUvD@]O]
