FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781222570
OL,3,CScotland have 'really good prospects'
OL,4,Cfor World Cup, says optimistic Swinney
OL,6,FAsked how he would rate Scotland's
OL,7,Fchances of winning the first three
OL,8,Fgames, he said: "I think we've got
OL,9,Freally good prospects, we've got a
OL,10,Fgreat squad.
OL,12,F"As I watched them play on Saturday, I
OL,13,Fthought they were demonstrating a lot
OL,14,Fof precision and they were working
OL,15,Fvery much together.
OL,17,F"There was a huge level of energy in
OL,18,Fthe team. It was a swelteringly hot
OL,19,Fnight, and they were performing really
OL,20,Fwell in those conditions.
OL,26,@pD@QOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
