OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781222570
OL,3,CScotland have 'really good prospects'
OL,4,Cfor World Cup, says optimistic Swinney
OL,6,F"So, I go into this very optimistic...
OL,7,Fthat the team's got great chances,
OL,8,Fgreat prospects, great strength and,
OL,9,Fcrucially, they are working together,
OL,10,Fand Scotland is right behind them."
